  18 Jul 2014; Maxim Koltsov <maksbotan@gentoo.org> aegisub-3.1.2.ebuild,
  aegisub-3.1.3.ebuild, aegisub-9999.ebuild:
  Fix linguas handling, bug #512924. Thanks to Nikoli.

*aegisub-3.1.3 (10 Jun 2014)

  10 Jun 2014; Maxim Koltsov <maksbotan@gentoo.org> +aegisub-3.1.3.ebuild,
  -aegisub-3.0.3.ebuild, -aegisub-3.0.4.ebuild, -aegisub-3.1.0.ebuild,
  aegisub-3.1.2.ebuild, aegisub-9999.ebuild:
  Bump to 3.1.3, update live ebuild, clean old, enable fftw by default in 3.1.3,
  bug #511896. Thanks to Nikoli.

  09 Jun 2014; Maxim Koltsov <maksbotan@gentoo.org> aegisub-3.1.2.ebuild:
  Update icon cache and desktop database, bug #508116. Respect LINGUAS, bug
  #508118. Fix sandbox access violation with openal, bug #508184. Thanks to
  Nikoli.

  04 Feb 2014; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> aegisub-3.1.2.ebuild,
  aegisub-9999.ebuild:
  Force USE="nls" enabled for boost wrt #498836 by "Nikoli"

*aegisub-3.1.2 (04 Feb 2014)

  04 Feb 2014; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> +aegisub-3.1.2.ebuild:
  Version bump by "Nikoli" at Freenode

*aegisub-3.1.0 (07 Jan 2014)

  07 Jan 2014; Tom Wijsman <TomWij@gentoo.org> +aegisub-3.1.0.ebuild,
  aegisub-9999.ebuild:
  Version bump to 3.1.0. Fix up dependencies as the package now requires
  wxGTK-3.x, icu and boost; fixes bug #493494, proxied commit for Nikoli.

  13 Oct 2013; Tom Wijsman <TomWij@gentoo.org> aegisub-3.0.4.ebuild,
  aegisub-9999.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  Applied sub slot operators on media-libs/ffmpegsource dependency, prevented
  EGIT_SOURCEDIR and S variables from looping in 9999 ebuild; proxied commit for
  Nikoli.

